lead_paragraph: Abdel Nader scored 19 points, Georges Niang added 17 with 10 rebounds and No. 21 Iowa State held off Oklahoma State 58-50 on Monday night in Niang's final home game.

headline.print_headline: No. 21 Iowa State Beats Oklahoma State 58-50
